27
00:02:45,950 --> 00:02:46,730
Hello, boss.

28
00:02:48,100 --> 00:02:49,829
Mr. Zhou, what brings you here?

29
00:02:50,130 --> 00:02:52,170
Can't I come to see the shooting of Feiran's commercials?

30
00:02:52,170 --> 00:02:54,230
