Action.

40
00:03:27,650 --> 00:03:28,910
Camera B, Camera B, follow up.

41
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:30,500
Jiayang, Jiayang, good, good, good.

42
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:32,160
Keep going, keep going.

43
